user_prompt_template:
Aggregate the following file analyses to create a comprehensive project understanding for chart planning:

**Aggregated Summaries:**
{aggregated_summaries}

**Dependency Graph:**
```json
{dependency_graph}
```

**Chart Hints from Analysis:**
{chart_hints}

---

Provide a comprehensive summary in the following JSON format:

```json
{
    "project_summary": "<Comprehensive summary of the project architecture and structure>",
    "main_components": [
        {
            "name": "<Component name>",
            "description": "<What this component does>",
            "relationships": ["<List of related components>"]
        }
    ],
    "data_flows": [
        "<Description of major data flows in the project>"
    ],
    "recommended_charts": [
        {
            "chart_type": "<flowchart/sequence/class/state/architecture/etc>",
            "title": "<Suggested chart title>",
            "description": "<What this chart should show>",
            "target_components": ["<Components to include>"]
        }
    ],
    "key_relationships": [
        "<Important relationships between components>"
    ]
}
```

Focus on:
1. Overall project architecture
2. Key component relationships
3. Main process flows
4. Recommended diagrams that would best represent the project
